description: As some of you may remember, I fucked a really cute fitness coach not long ago. The guy was amazing so you can imagine how happy I was when he gave me a call. He needed money and was willing to bring a friend. This friend was a Russian exchange student, who got to Prague recently. He wanted to work on his physique and that's how he met the coach. They both needed money badly and decided to ask me for help. I had no problem with that, a threesome is always a good idea. There was a little language barrier between us but we managed. The guy understood a little bit and the meaning of my requests was fairly obvious. As a little foreplay, I let them kiss and play with each other. After a while I couldn't take it anymore and stepped in. I really think that everyone involved had a very nice time.
title: Czech Hunter 475
